  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you choose this technique at 2nd level, you begin specializing in skills to utilize your Puppet as a suit of armor.</p><p> You gain proficiency in Heavy armor and the Disguise kit.</p><p> Choose between the following upgrades: Chakra Blast, Integrated Weapon, or Power Fist.</p><p> You gain this Upgrade and it does not count against your total known Upgrades.</p><p> This chosen upgrade increases its damage die by 1 step.</p><p> Lastly, while wearing your Juggernaut Armor, you are able to qualify for jutsu that require you to wear armor of a specific type, regardless of your Juggernaut Armor's type.</p><p></p>",
